# Laser cutting services in Spain. We are specialists in precision laser cutting

Laser Galicia counts with large experience and technical capacity to manage complex projects that include laser cutting from our facility in Spain.

[Contact us](https://lasergalicia.com/en/contact-us/)

### Sheet metal laser cutting

**High precision sheet metal laser cutting** for a perfect assembly without any readjustments.

### Tube laser cutting

The **cutting of tubes** by laser means the revolution of the design of metal structures, that helps to reduce the assembly and welding times.

### Sheet Metal Bending

The **bending of metals sheets** replaces the processes of assembly and welding by an intelligent design that includes bends with different radius.

### Welding

The **manual welding** gives us the capability of manufacturing fully finished parts made from plate and tube. We also have a robotic cell to manufacture series.

## Advantages of laser cutting

The **laser cutting** process offers several advantages, below you can see the main ones:

### High precision and accuracy

The laser technology performs cuts much more precise and detailed, even in small parts or parts with complex geometries

### Clean cuts and without sharp edges

The laser cutting technology performs clean cuts without sharp edges, which avoids the need of any reworks to obtain a better finishing

### Less material deformation

The non-contact nature of the laser cutting process reduces the thermal deformation of the parts. The focused beam achieves a narrow cut width, while local heating allows minimal heat input.

### Materials versatility

Laser cutting is suitable for a diversity of metals and thicknesses. At Laser Galicia we laser cut parts in a wide range of material grades of carbon steel, stainless steel, aluminum, copper and brass.

![](https://lasergalicia.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Laser-Galicia10.jpg)

### Automation and programming

The laser cutting machines are programmed and automated to perform serial cut in a much more precise way

### Less material waste

Precise cuts minimize the material waste, optimizing the resources and reducing the costs.

## Quality matters

We keep the highest quality standards for all the projects we perform. We are proud of offering a fast and efficient service that meets the most demanding requirements, and that is backed by the diverse quality certificates we have implemented.

[Discover them](https://lasergalicia.com/en/quality/)
